que selling proposition here and we have very, very strong clinical data. And I think that’s testament to the fact that we hope to get approval by the end of July. So we’ll be ready to go. We’ll be working on educational programs. We’ll have programs to help build awareness of the disease state with a long-term impact of the disease state prior launch. We’ll be having a lot of public relations efforts, so Dr. Bailes will be available to the media upon launch and the brand’s spokesperson. And we will be able to cover 2,500 hospitals I think very efficiently and very effectively with the sales force in place.
