Insider Activity


Individual




Scott L. Tarriff



Mr. Scott L. Tarriff is on the Board of Directors at ZIOPHARM Oncology, Inc., Synthetic Biologics, Inc. and Eagle Pharmaceuticals, Inc. Mr. Tarriff was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by Par Pharmaceutical, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer by Par Pharmaceutical Cos., Inc., and Senior Director-Marketing by Bristol-Myers Squibb Co. He also served on the board at Clinical Data, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from The Pennsylvania State University and an MBA from Rider University.



